item.title: By: Paula

item.description: Lake Michigan it's a fantastic song! I feel so up, when i listen. I'm from brazil, and someday if they could come here i will be for sure in their show! Love the band, and sucess for them! see... rhimes!

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: I really enjoyed <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rogue_Wave_(band)" rel="nofollow">Out of the Shadow</a>, but nothing they've done since has really appealed to me. I can see why Subpop lost interest.
item.content:encoded: I really enjoyed Out of the Shadow, but nothing they’ve done since has really appealed to me. I can see why Subpop lost interest.
